  "title": "Planning Engineer (Building Facilities, Primavera)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Participate in the development and management of the Project Work Schedule, covering building works, M&amp;E, and Process Systems, from concept design through construction/installation to testing and commissioning.</li>\n  <li>Estimate the duration and resource requirements for key construction activities.</li>\n  <li>Prepare technical documentation for tender submissions.</li>\n  <li>Contribute to site planning, work scheduling, and monitoring of site implementation progress.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 4 years of experience in <strong>planning construction projects</strong> for <strong>building facilities.</strong></li>\n  <li>Good knowledge using <strong>Primavera.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
